                                   java.lang.String... values)
        Deprecated. 
        Saves a pack of strings to some attribute. I.e: [tag attr="value"]
        Parameters:
        parent - parent element (where to add newly created tags)
        nodeName - node name (tag, in our example)
        attrName - attribute name (attr, in our example)
        values - a pack of values to add
